				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The player examines a mysterious, ornate box in their possession. If the player is Shadowheart, she'll know she has to take care of this item and get it to Baldur's Gate. The player can also try to discard the box or force it open, but cannot. Companions chime in with their thoughts if present."
